Text Content: Indian Summer Monsoon Rainfall (ISMR) during August-Sept. over the country as a whole is likely to be normal with 101% (43.1 cm) of All-India Rainfall (AIR) of long-term mean of 42.9 cm.The monthly-predicted AIRs are 23.7 cm (93%) and 19.4 cm (111%) for the months of August & September respectively
